Comment: 0,0:00:00.45,0:00:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:00:02.45,0:00:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这次这个项目开始的契机
Comment: 0,0:00:05.55,0:00:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是去年 Anime Expo 时　我们经 Crunchyroll 介绍认识了 Porter 先生
Comment: 0,0:00:14.99,0:00:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我们第一次见面
Comment: 0,0:00:17.30,0:00:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.30,0:00:20.96,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,This is my third or fourth trip to meet with A-1 Pictures,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.96,0:00:24.08,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,who is the studio that's developing this short film.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.08,0:00:26.88,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,I had no idea when I walked into that room for the first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.88,0:00:30.16,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,that I was gonna come back to Japan like seven or eight times that year,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.16,0:00:32.72,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,to meet with A-1 Pictures and continue to work on the video.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.72,0:00:34.02,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,And I had no idea that...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.02,0:00:38.09,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,...it was gonna be one of the most artistically fulfilling thing I've ever got to do in my life.
Comment: 0,0:00:38.35,0:00:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:00:38.35,0:00:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,老实说　我们当时也怀疑过我们能否成功完成这一项目
Comment: 0,0:00:43.92,0:00:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但是当 Porter 先生第一次来日本时
Comment: 0,0:00:47.53,0:00:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们发现 Porter 先生是位真诚友善的人
Comment: 0,0:00:50.70,0:00:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,而且感受到了他对日本动画发自内心的喜爱
Comment: 0,0:00:54.60,0:00:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,就觉得无论如何得为他完成这项工作
Comment: 0,0:00:56.64,0:00:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,于是我们开始了这一项目
Comment: 0,0:00:59.11,0:01:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.11,0:01:03.59,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,To be able to write the story and to see it come to life in front of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.59,0:01:05.82,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,It's...I cannot describe the feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.51,0:01:21.70,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,Initial conversations that we had when we first met with them,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.70,0:01:25.55,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,I think it was a perfect way for us to get this mutual understanding of...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.55,0:01:27.42,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,something that's really serious,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.42,0:01:31.04,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,and we want this thing to have a lot of integrity, and we want it to be really beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.04,0:01:34.19,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,The look that I wanted to go for was very much like A-1 style.
Comment: 0,0:01:31.04,0:01:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:01:34.41,0:01:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,和我们这些一直从事动画制作的人们比起来　Porter 先生还能体会到有所不同的东西
Comment: 0,0:01:41.68,0:01:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这对于我们来说是一种很强的刺激
Comment: 0,0:01:44.85,0:01:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,从而期待通过合作　能创作出有新意的与众不同的作品
Comment: 0,0:01:51.36,0:02:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.36,0:02:00.70,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,The video for Shelter is the most concrete distillation of being completely immersed into fantasy,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.70,0:02:06.37,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,and the wierd ways that's connecting with reality nowdays with like virtual reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.37,0:02:13.95,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,and the fact that most of our experience of life now is in some way connected to technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.95,0:02:17.60,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,The world of Shelter, this virtual reality universe that she's stuck in,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.60,0:02:21.12,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,where she has this super power to create environments,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.12,0:02:23.62,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,and go around and play in them and explore them every day,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.62,0:02:25.93,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,just think that it's a really really beautiful notion,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.93,0:02:30.46,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,and something that's really dear and relevant to my own sensibility as an artist.
Comment: 0,0:02:25.92,0:02:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:02:30.46,0:02:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这部 MV 正如前面所说
Comment: 0,0:02:33.70,0:02:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是过去从未尝试过的形式和出发点以及方式方法　这些东西聚集在了一起
Comment: 0,0:02:41.27,0:02:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.37,0:02:46.90,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,The nature of working with animation is that you need to be involved in every step of the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.90,0:02:52.84,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,From character designs, and environment designs, and writing the story,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.84,0:02:56.34,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,and then actually storyboarding it, and then doing animatics.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.34,0:02:59.34,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,You need to be very very close to the process,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.34,0:03:02.49,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,because you can't ask for changes once you have something finished to look at.
Comment: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:03:02.76,0:03:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,要说这个项目中最有趣的地方
Comment: 0,0:03:06.27,0:03:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,在于从来没有过的合作方和艺术家
Comment: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,以及制作方式和团队构成
Comment: 0,0:03:13.64,0:03:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,能在这样的环境下完成工作是非常有趣的
Comment: 0,0:03:15.94,0:03:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.94,0:03:19.72,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,I wanted to pick up a popular name. I liked Rin a lot for this character, I liked that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:23.24,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,Just so happenes that the CEO of A-1 Pictures' daughter is named Rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.24,0:03:26.80,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,which meant they took a real liking to the charater into the project.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.80,0:03:28.18,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,And when I found that out,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.18,0:03:30.57,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,I was like "Oh wow! OK, that's too weird, we can change the charater name."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.57,0:03:33.76,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,They were like "No, don't...keep it, keep it as Rin."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.76,0:03:35.45,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,which I was really happy with.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.65,0:03:42.69,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,You will be amazed by just how even their drafts and sketches, how incredible those looked.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.69,0:03:45.72,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,There were so many conversations about what Rin's room would look like.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.72,0:03:49.88,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,Viewers won't see 90% of those sketches,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.88,0:03:53.00,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,and though barely see her room in the animation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.49,0:03:57.15,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,It's a really really extensive process.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.15,0:04:02.60,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,The only surprise for me having worked on other animation projects before...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.60,0:04:06.50,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,...was just the incredible level of quality to which A-1 did it.
Comment: 0,0:04:06.50,0:04:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:04:06.56,0:04:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得这个项目中最有趣之处就在于 Porter 先生本人
Comment: 0,0:04:14.03,0:04:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,诸如为何他创作出了那样的音乐　为何受人喜爱
Comment: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,以及他创作上的热情和想象力
Comment: 0,0:04:27.65,0:04:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.35,0:04:34.16,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,To actually collaborate on creating anime is just...it's unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.16,0:04:38.90,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,And...I had several moments when I was in their studios,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.90,0:04:43.71,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,where I was just like..."this is happening right now, I'm getting to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.71,0:04:49.02,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,I'm like getting to work with these people, and create this character,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.02,0:04:52.16,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,this girl in this universe in this story.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.74,0:04:59.55,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,I had a moment where I was like "You know what, even if the world can never see this video,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.55,0:05:02.19,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,the process alone would have made it all worth it."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.19,0:05:04.64,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,For me the fact that people gonna get to see this,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.64,0:05:10.20,Porter-eng,,0,0,0,,beyond just me saying it, it's even more incredible.
